title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 9 2021

description:
OutKick's Joe Kinsey discusses his exclusive interview with UPenn swimmers on the transgender story.


Kayleigh McEnany, former White House Press Secretary under Trump, on the big issues of the day.


This is how it starts: NYC to give illegal aliens voting rights.


Kentucky Senator Rand Paul shares what his family does to prepare for Christmas (hint: it involves the Constitution) and other covid news.
